 index.html | 10 +++++-----
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/index.html b/index.html
index 49d863b..dbbf050 100644
--- a/index.html
+++ b/index.html
@@ -2977,15 +2977,15 @@
         <div class="chat-inner">
             <div class="section-eyebrow">The chat channel</div>
             <h2 class="section-heading">Chat that opens the conversation.</h2>
-            <p class="section-lede lx-desk">One of LUPO's four channels, and the first one visitors meet. Most chatbots sit and wait. LUPO opens the moment someone lands, tuned to the page they're on and the visitors it already knows. Drag to compare.</p>
-            <p class="section-lede lx-mob">One of LUPO's four channels, and the first visitors meet. It opens first, instead of waiting. Drag to compare.</p>
+            <p class="section-lede lx-desk">LUPO's chat is one of four inbound channels. It opens the conversation, qualifies against your ICP, and carries the same context as web form, email, and phone. Drag to compare.</p>
+            <p class="section-lede lx-mob">LUPO's chat is one of four inbound channels, carrying the same context as web form, email, and phone. Drag to compare.</p>
 
