-                        <div class="chat-panel-sub">Drag the divider. Right is LUPO. Left is the chatbot your competitor still runs.</div>
+                        <div class="chat-panel-title">From first reply to qualified lead.</div>
+                        <div class="chat-panel-sub">Generic chat answers questions. LUPO qualifies pipeline. Drag the divider, right is LUPO, left is the chatbot your competitor still runs.</div>
                     </div>
                     <div class="cmp-stage" data-cmp>
                         <!-- under layer: the generic bot -->
@@ -3035,7 +3035,7 @@
                 <div class="chat-panel">
                     <div class="chat-panel-head">
                         <div class="chat-panel-title">7&times; faster than Fin.</div>
-                        <div class="chat-panel-sub">Same question, same instant. LUPO answers before the other agent finishes typing.</div>
+                        <div class="chat-panel-sub">Same question, same instant. LUPO replies before the other agent finishes typing.</div>
